{"tid":1380112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想同大家講 今次係我地爭取真普選嘅最後機會","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:29.000Z","uid":220864,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf35c41ce4521f91a677fbc2354b945dfecf06f","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"每次開po講話要爭取真普選<br />\n<br />\n總會有班人衝出嚟話<br />\n爭取普選係需要長時間/唔係而家要爭取嘅<br />\n<br />\n我想問你諗住用幾多年爭取? 5年? 10年?<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知10年可以多左近45萬單程證落嚟香港<br />\n每年都多5萬幾人<br />\n重要佢地住夠7年就可以擁有投票權<br />\n你想等到佢地有投票權？<br />\n<br />\n你再拖落去，我信架，有朝一日你會爭取到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係有份投票嘅已經大部分唔係香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n所以去到而家呢一刻<br />\n我地唔單止行動要升級<br />\n訴求都要升級<br />\n<br />\n一個一定要得到先可以代表我地勝利嘅結果<br />\n就算得到獨立調查委員會又好<br />\n就算佢講明話撒回都好<br />\n我地都唔以退<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要真普選</span>係我地唯一嘅目標<br />\n<br />\n補充資料: 2018年選民登記冊上有3,814,318名選民<br />\n2017: 3,805,069<br />\n2016: 3,779,085<br />\n<br />\n當然唔係全部上升都係新移民<br />\n我信有學生年滿18歲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係香港生育率低<br />\n你覺得入面有幾多成就18歲成人？"},{"pid":"464256bfcfafea194acab7bd7224b6319df0d2b5","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdd1ffc10b880c2e31f50088b5dfff649b7430d","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:15.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"709ebe42df6178853c52ee532390149f328b9947","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"fe82cc2431e1dadfd0ecc6033fa3a98a7122d9c3","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"1340020fb5d7e194378226eaa4b38f43e8a5e544","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"26a116abd787a1cb398ba633e097c2bbafefbdf8","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:55.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"834a94e477dfdb3f059ab302d605ffb3bd28a12f","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fef505a4a7899da6edeb74022d510db87cb682a7","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"34bdc8840e2eeef71045b338bc3688131ecf8cce","tid":1380112,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e534f23b047702047f7db625e9b8f6b59566e92c","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"32ce2502a759948dcb2d8751f0fe387ca4de7d6a","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bb58166068ee2dd54f2f61c38533d4efb5ac6dbd","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7245134a8272b7918f1b0cd8af53e80cc24c59ec","tid":1380112,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"十年<br />\n十連"},{"pid":"9e7d6cc9